feat: Refactor settings management components and introduce file settings
- Updated import paths for SiteInfo and PageSittingInfo types to a centralized type file. - Added new FileSettingsForm component to manage file-related settings. - Implemented various subcomponents for file settings including FileUploadSettings, MediaExtractorSettings, and ThumbnailGeneratorSettings. - Enhanced PageSittingForm and BaseInfoForm to accommodate new file settings. - Introduced a new interface FileSettingsInfo to define file configuration structure. - Updated the main settings management index.vue to include file settings tab and form. - Refactored form handling to integrate file settings into the reactive form structure. - Improved UI with collapsible sections for better organization of settings.
